   117→/**
   118→ * Handles database errors consistently across all resolvers
   119→ *
   120→ * @param error - The error thrown by the database operation
   121→ * @param config - Configuration for error handling
   122→ * @throws Always throws a user-friendly error
   123→ *
   124→ * @example
